{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "jo tas Klings KUNGS buhe\nprett jums weens Leezineeks/ tas\nKlings no ta Namma farwas\nSwehtibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "3. Jo rangi/ tas KUNGS\niseet no tawas Weetas/ wiꞥſch\nnolaideſees un stahwehs us tahs\nSemmes Augstumeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "4. Un tee Kalni iſkuffihs ap-\npakſch winna/ un tahs Eeleijas\ntaps ſaplohſitas ka Waskis no\nta Uggunis/ ka Uhdens/ kas uhs\nLetju tohp iſgabſts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "5. Scho wiſſi darrihs wiꞥſch\nJehkaba Pahrkahpschanas deht/\nun to Israëta Behrnu Grehku\ndeht. Bet kurra irr Jehkaba\nPahrkahpchana? Neggi Sa-\nmarija? Un kurri irr tee Angstu-\nmi Juhda? Neggi Jerusaleme?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Tapehz darriſchu es Sa-\nmariju par Akminzu Kohpu Lau-\nká / par Dehſtſchanas Weetu\nweenâ Wihna Dahrsá/ un es no-\ngahſichn winna Akminus Ee-\nleijá/ un atklaſchhu winnas Pa-\nnattus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Un wiſſi winnas Deevek-\nki taps ſagrausti / un wiſſas\nwinnas Mauku Mantas taps\nar Uggunis ſadedſinatas/ un wiſ-\nfus winnas Elka-Deewus darri-\nſchu es par weenn Tuhtnesi / jo\ntee irr no Mauku-Algas ſakra-\nti/ un taps atkat par Mauku-\nAlgu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Pahr tcho irr man jabeḥ\najabe un jarauda/ es eetchu ap-\naupihts un knils/ es behdaschohe\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ka tee Puſki/ un baiſſchohs ta\njaunt Stranti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "9. Jo winnas Mohzibas irr\nnahwigas/ jo tee irr lihds Ju-\nda nahkutchas/ wiꞥſch ſteepjabs\nlihds manno Lauschu Wahrtim/\nlihds Jerusalemet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "10. Ne fluddinajeet to eeſch\nGattas/ ne raudajt tik ganschi/\nwahrtajtees Pihschlôs Pihschlu\nNaimmá.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "11. Atsetj tu Eedsihwotaja ta\nſkaista (Pilsfahta/) ar atſegta\nKaunuuna/ ta Eedsihwotaja no\nZaënana ne iſees: Schehloſcha-\nna irr Tuwaka Naimmá/ kas no\njums tawn Uſturreſchannu dabbu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Jo ta Eedsihwotaja no\nMarota ſkumjabs pahr to (no-\nsudduſchu) Labbuunu/ ka tas\nLaunnms irr no ta KUNGA\nnonahzis/ lihds Jerusalemes\nWahrtim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Juhds Sirgus preekſch\nRatteein tu Eedsihwotaja no\nLakifa / (ſchis irr tas Gefahkuns\nto Grehku tahs Zianas Meitas/)\nka eeſch tewin irr Israëta\nPahrkahpschanas atraſtas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Tadeht fuhti Dahwanas\nuhs Maresett eeſch Gattas. Tee\nNammi no Akſiva taps teem\nIsraëta Rehnixeempar Melleem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Es atweediſchu tew tu\nEedsihwotaja no Maresas weh-\nweenu Mantneeku/ wiꞥſch nahks\nlihds Adullamam/ lihds Israëta\nGohdam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Darrajs piſſu/ un no-\nzehtreeß tarvo iſluttinatu Behr-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
